Software


Altitude Group plc provide SAAS and online personalisation solutions for the promotional products industry. From the sourcing portal with products from hundreds of trade suppliers and professional end user websites to innovative business manage software, smaller distributors are equipped with the tools they need to not only get their business off the ground, but to successfully grow in a competitive market.




Exhibitions


Altitude Group plc host the highly acclaimed Promotional Product Expo, attracting thousands of distributors and hundreds of top suppliers making it the biggest show in the industry calendar. They also host the more intimate Promotional Product Road shows throughout the year, designed to get build lasting relationships between distributors and suppliers.




Publications


Altitude Group plc provide effective marketing tools that are designed to improve data flow between suppliers and distributors. Spectrum and Envoy are two end user catalogues with 3000+ customers in over 10 countries and include products from hundreds of trade suppliers, and PPD, the industry’s magazine with a 5,000 readership list.




Enterprise Solutions


Altitude Group plc provide a range of Enterprise Solutions for the more larger, established companies including Customer Focus Enterprise, an in-depth business management system with modular upgrades and Customer Focus Enterprise Web Stores, sophisticated websites that are designed to take your company to the next level.











