About Altitude Group PLC 

Altitude Group Plc is the leading provider of technology and information services to the promotional products, print and clothing industries which operates brands that provide information, data and enterprise level technology through a Software as a Service (“SaaS”) model.


Customer Focus Software Ltd (UK)
Customer Focus provides key marketing and technology tools on an international scale to both suppliers and distributors operating in the promotional merchandise industry, catering to over 3000 customers in over 10 countries.
Customer Focus specialises in media, marketing and technology solutions for the development of the promotional product and print industries, offering a market leading and internationally acclaimed collection of technology tools and marketing / publishing services designed to help grow sales and profits of promotional product suppliers distributors. These tools include exhibitions, catalogues, search portals, magazines, websites and business management software. The head office is currently located in Manchester, along with a full technical support team in Sheffield, UK.


Customer Focus, Inc. (USA)
Customer Focus, Inc. provides a range of Cloud-based Ecommerce, Enterprise Resource Planning, Customer Relationship Management and web-based solutions to both suppliers and distributors operating in the promotional merchandise industry, with sales, development and support staff based in Costa Mesa, California. They deliver one system to manage all of your key business processes reducing key strokes, improving customer service and cutting costs.
Customer Focus, Inc. also provides information services to the industry including product data flow between suppliers and independent distributors, working with leading US distributors since 2007 to help reduce costs, win more orders, and improve their customer service.


Customer Focus Enterprise
Customer Focus Enterprise is our Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) software for larger promotional product distributors and suppliers, and print brokers and managers.
Since 1999, hundreds of customers and thousands of users in the UK, Europe and USA have invested in Customer Focus Enterprise, gaining a highly comprehensive and robust business management system, complete with integrated web stores and punch-out capabilities.
The head office is in Sheffield, England, along with an additional office in the USA. The development support teams are based in the UK.


Customer Focus Interactive Imaging
As the leading global provider of virtual sample technology, Technologo is trusted by leading manufacturers, suppliers and distributors of Promotional Products around the world.
With over 15 years of software development and innovation at its core, Technologo has created a wide range of interactive image solutions that are proven to drive increased engagement from online B2B and B2C buyers, reduced cart abandonment rates and increased average order values.
As part of the Customer Focus Interactive Imaging division, Technologo integrates seamlessly with Artworktool, the patented artwork creation and sharing solution, increasing operational efficiency alongside the improved customer experience that benefits users in 180 countries who collectively create more than one million virtual samples each month.
Our dedicated and talented team comprises of photographers, graphic artists and software engineers that are focused on creating the most user friendly, easy-to-use, device agnostic image management solutions available, accessible from any browser, on any platform.
































